channel.title: [317 Delta]Quoted Upon All - Now 317 Delta
channel.description:
[b][u]Base[/u][/b]: 317 Delta
[B][SIZE=5]Information/Features:[/SIZE][/B]
[u][b]Miscellaneous[/b][/u]
[ul][li]NPC's in ordinary places[/li] [li]Correct NPC drops[/li] [li]Pick Wheat Option[/li] [li]Pick Potato Option[/li] [li]Pick Cabbage Option[/li] [li]All doors in Lumbridge, Varrock and Falador[/li] [li]Dupe Proof[/li] [li]574kb Client.java[/li] [li]Jad[/li] [li]Bounty Hunter[/li] [li]Flower Game[/li][/ul]
[u][b]Melee/Range/Mage (including weapons, weapon animations, etc.)[/b][/u]
[ul][li]Perfect Combat[/li] [li]PK Following[/li] [li]Dragon Claws + Its Animation 100%[/li] [li]Staff of Light[/li] [li]525 Animations[/li] [li]100% Barrelchest Anchor[/li][/ul]
[u][b] Skills[/b][/u]
[ul][li]Tree Spirit[/li] [li]All Skills Working[/li] [li]Theiving Stalls[/ul]
[center][B][SIZE=5]Pictures/Images:[/SIZE][/B]
Dragon Scimitar Special
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/2075118/Dragon_Scimitar_Special.gif][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/2075118/Dragon_Scimitar_Special.gif[/img][/url]
Dragon Dagger Special
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/2075120/DDS.gif][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/2075120/DDS.gif[/img][/url]
Abyssal Whip Moves and Special
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/2075131/abby.gif][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/2075131/abby.gif[/img][/url]
Armadyl Godsword Special
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/2075134/AGS.gif][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/2075134/AGS.gif[/img][/url]
Bandos Godsword Special
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/2075136/BGS.gif][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/2075136/BGS.gif[/img][/url]
Dragon Longsword, Granite Maul, Saradomin Godsword, Zamorak Godsword, and Dragon Halberd
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/2075140/HalberdLongswordMaulSaradominZamorak.gif][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/2075140/HalberdLongswordMaulSaradominZamorak.gif[/img][/url][/center]
I am deciding to make this tiny project for fun (since I love working solo). I want to test my ability to code, and this will be my test, and you'll be my judges :). I believe that this will be a good, nice, clean base for 317 delta users. Wanna know my 100% total reason for choosing 317? Shhh, but i think 2008 is the time of PKing. It brought out the beasts, and the awesomeness of RS PKing. So, this Delta may have 474 stuff to make my favorite time of PKing.
My aim to is make an amazing PKing source, that's also not messy.
[u][b]Aren't you working on Brotherhood and T.U.PK.S?[/b][/u]
Yeah, but this is a tiny little project that shouldn't take 1 - 2 months to finish.
[b] XMIKEIX:[/b] A nice base to start with [b]Arham 4:[/b] Using his time to make this. [b]Realm Onwards:[/b] Inspiring me to code. This project (my project) pumped me up alot and to be focused and determined about things. [b]lostmyphat:[/b] Updates of February 12th.
